interactivity.requirements: You must be on at least Day  153  to unlock this Event. You must have seen or permanently missed the following Events: Seen Main Events up to " A Proper Introduction "
interactivity.to_get_this_event: Autoplay during weekday if requirements are met

progression.synopsis: Sensei and some students help Molly move her things into her new dorm room. However, Maya is tired, Ami is trying to rescue a bird , and Sensei is unable to help because Molly has a strict no-boys-allowed policy regarding her things — as such, Rin has been doing most of the actual lifting. Sensei, Molly, and Rin talk for a while about Rin's participation in roleplaying games (to be kept secret from Chika at all costs), Sensei's proper title, and the upcoming beach trip. Meanwhile, Ami has been unable to reach the bird — Sensei tells her that it "lives here now".

changelog: This Event was added in Update 0.7.
